<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīśakavarṣaṁbulu 1344
<lb n="2"/>Agunēṁṭi śubhakṛtsaṁvatsara kārtti
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ka kṛṣṇa tadīyyānu bhānuvāramu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>nāṁḍu śrīviṣṇuvardhanamahā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rājulaina śrīnarasiṁhadēvacakrava
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rttulu tamakuṁ buṇyārdhtamugānu
<lb n="7"/>Āyuṣmatsuputrāvāptigānunnu
<lb n="8"/>ciṁttitamanōradavāptigānunnu
<lb n="9"/>paṁcadhārala dharmmēśvaramahādē
<lb n="10" break="no"/>varaku Agaṁḍadīpānakuṁ beṭṭina go 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṟelu 50 mānadīpamu naḍapi bōI
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ṁḍu battuni pōlebōyini koḍuku
<lb n="13"/>Ayitana bōyiniki kaluvalapa
<lb n="14" break="no"/>lli polānarācaĪḍatūrppuna jītapuṁ
<lb n="15"/>baṭṭulalōnu cēnu na 10 nnu Ācaṁdrā
<lb n="16" break="no"/>rkamavunaṭṭugānu peṭṭiri <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> yi narasihya
<lb n="17" break="no"/>dēvacakravartulē Ī dinamaṁdunu dharma
<lb n="18" break="no"/>liṁgānaku paṁcavaktrakōhaḷi bhaṁgārā
<lb n="19" break="no"/>naṁ jēyiṁci samarppiṁpiri <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī nara
<lb n="20" break="no"/>siṁhyadēvacakravarttuladēvulaina vīra
<lb n="21" break="no"/>kaṁgāru dharmaliṁgamunaku Akha
<lb n="22" break="no"/>ṁḍadīpānaku goṟiyalu 50 samarppiṁ
<lb n="23" break="no"/>pi mānadīpamu naḍapi bōyiṁḍu
<lb n="24"/>pōtanabōyini koḍuku gaṁḍebō
<lb n="25" break="no"/>yiniki <unclear>ve</unclear>lucūri Āvalōnu cēnu 10
<lb n="26"/>veṭṭiri <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

